Dependencies
============

libcurl
libcrypto (openssl)
asio c++ networking library
boost c++ libraries
libsqlite3 database library
libgtkmm-2.4 c++ gtk wrapper library

Ubuntu Dependencies
===================

These are the debian packages you need if
you are running an Ubuntu based distribution.

libcurl4-openssl-dev
libboost-all-dev
libasio-dev
libssl-dev
libsqlite3-dev
libgtkmm-2.4-dev

Installation
============

1. Type `make clean ; make`
